---
title: ISBN Metadata Lookup Chain
---
flowchart TD
    A(["ISBN entered"]) --> B[Normalize & validate]
    B --> C{Checksum valid?}
    C -->|No| D["Show validation error"]
    D --> E["Manual entry<br/>(always available)"]
    C -->|Yes| F["Query Open Library"]
    F --> G{Found useful<br/>metadata?}
    G -->|Yes| H["Return metadata<br/>Provider: Open Library"]
    G -->|No / Unavailable| I["Query Let Books<br/>metadata API"]
    I --> J{Found useful<br/>metadata?}
    J -->|Yes| K["Return metadata<br/>Provider: Let Books API"]
    J -->|No / Unavailable| E

    style H fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32
    style K fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32
    style E fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#e65100
    style D fill:#ffebee,stroke:#c62828
